{"tid":1657195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"VTC 主任鄺國傑以「曱甴」形容示威者","createTime":"2019-10-16T03:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T04:32:45.000Z","uid":216788,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ab04b0ae15a3dbbe3405bb7ee32af1c43a0e976a","tid":1657195,"uid":216788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T03:34:37.000Z","msg":"香港知專設計學院學生陳彥霖早前被發現浮屍海面，大批職訓局學生連日到學院集會，要求公開CCTV片段還原真相，其間有人不滿校方未有清晰交代事件，在校舍內進行破壞。《蘋果》取得一張由職訓局人員發出的內部電郵截圖，發文者提醒校內職員今日或有人到校示威，<span style=\"color: red;\">電郵中刻意以「cockroaches（蟑螂）」一詞形容示威者。職訓局回覆時稱該電郵是「個別員工訊息」、「純屬個人表述」，沒回應會否跟進事件。 </span><br />\n<br />\n據了解，涉事電郵由職訓局設施管理主任<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鄺國傑</span></span></strong>以英文撰寫、今午以機構員工電郵寄予各校舍多名職員，主要提醒或有人會到校示威，如發現破壞行為便立即報警，指該局的EHSD（產業管理及健康安全科）會全力支援各校舍；不過撰文者刻意在電郵中的示威者字眼後加上「cockroaches」作形容。有局內職員輾轉看到截圖，批評發文者寫法荒謬，「（撰文者）都唔知自己做緊咩！」記者曾多次致電鄺國傑，不過無人接聽。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSources : <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191015/60157625?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F60157625%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVlFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=c1fec4f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191015%2F60157625%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_article_share%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dshare_link&h=b14fba3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191015/60157625?utm_campaign=hkad_article_share&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=share_link</a>"},{"pid":"205d43ffdf1124bbdecef5c